15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 6-101.6b, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 6-101.6b. A. For purposes of this section, "teacher":
18 1. "Teacher" means the term as defined in paragraph 1 of
19 Section 1-116 of Title 70 of the Oklahoma Statutes this title; and
20 2. "Support employee" means the term as defined in paragraph 9
21 of Section 1-116 of this title.
22 B. No school district shall prohibit or take disciplinary
23 action against teachers or support employees for:
